00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:10.390 align:middle line:84%
In this video, we'll see how
to edit basic video properties.

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:12.970 align:middle line:84%
The Videos page provides
an easy-to-use interface

00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:15.670 align:middle line:84%
for managing the
videos in your account.

00:00:15.670 --> 00:00:20.240 align:middle line:84%
The body of the page will list
all the videos in the account.

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.030 align:middle line:84%
Clicking on a video title
will open the Video properties

00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:28.010 align:middle line:84%
page, where you can see
all the video properties.

00:00:28.010 --> 00:00:31.280 align:middle line:84%
The properties are
organized into sections.

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:34.670 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to edit the Video
Information properties.

00:00:34.670 --> 00:00:38.060 align:middle line:84%
To edit the properties,
click the Edit button,

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:40.920 align:middle line:90%
or double-click in a section.

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:44.250 align:middle line:84%
I'll start by adding
a short description.

00:00:44.250 --> 00:00:47.760 align:middle line:84%
I'm also going to assign
a video content type.

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.010 align:middle line:84%
By selecting a
video content type,

00:00:50.010 --> 00:00:52.140 align:middle line:84%
Brightcove can
compile your analytics

00:00:52.140 --> 00:00:55.890 align:middle line:84%
with those of similar videos and
provide more robust analytics,

00:00:55.890 --> 00:00:59.740 align:middle line:84%
like Brightcove's
Video Benchmark Score.

00:00:59.740 --> 00:01:01.980 align:middle line:84%
Finally, tags are
a set of keywords

00:01:01.980 --> 00:01:05.370 align:middle line:84%
that can be assigned to a
video and facilitate searching.

00:01:05.370 --> 00:01:06.540 align:middle line:90%
So I'll add some tags.

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:09.110 align:middle line:90%


00:01:09.110 --> 00:01:11.910 align:middle line:90%
When I'm done, I'll click Save.

00:01:11.910 --> 00:01:13.710 align:middle line:84%
To go back to the
list of videos,

00:01:13.710 --> 00:01:15.570 align:middle line:84%
I'll click the
Back to Videos link

00:01:15.570 --> 00:01:18.200 align:middle line:90%
in the top left of the page.

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:21.000 align:middle line:90%